text: Phormictopus auratus, commonly known as the Cuban bronze tarantula, is a species of tarantula endemic to Cuba. It is found in the provinces of Camagüey, Las Tunas and Holguín. == See also == * List of Theraphosidae species ==References== Category:Theraphosidae Category:Spiders of Cuba Category:Spiders described in 2005
title: Phormictopus auratus
